  number = {4},
  month = aug,
  abstract = {A general radiosity method accounting for all interreflections of
	light between diffuse and nondiffuse surfaces in complex environments
	is introduced. As contrasted with previous radiosity methods, surfaces
	are no longer required to be perfectly diffuse reflectors and emitters.
